@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber

AguiRestController -> AguiMvcController: AguiRestController鐨剅un()鏂规硶\n璋冪敤AguiMvcController鐨刪andle()鏂规硶
AguiMvcController -> AguiMvcController: AguiMvcController鐨刪andle()鏂规硶\n璋冪敤鑷韩鐨刪andleInternal()鏂规硶
AguiMvcController -> AguiRequestProcessor: AguiMvcController鐨刪andleInternal()鏂规硶\n璋冪敤AguiRequestProcessor鐨刾rocess()鏂规硶
AguiRequestProcessor -> DefaultAgentResolver: AguiRequestProcessor鐨刾rocess()鏂规硶璋冪敤\nDefaultAgentResolver鐨剅esolveAgent()鏂规硶鑾峰彇agent
DefaultAgentResolver -> AguiAgentRegistry: DefaultAgentResolver涓皟鐢ˋguiAgentRegistry鑾峰彇agent
DefaultAgentResolver <-- AguiAgentRegistry: AguiAgentRegistry杩斿洖agent
AguiRequestProcessor <-- DefaultAgentResolver: DefaultAgentResolver杩斿洖agent
AguiRequestProcessor -> AguiAgentAdapter: AguiRequestProcessor鐨刪andleInternal()鏂规硶\n璋冪敤AguiAgentAdapter鐨剅un()鏂规硶
AguiAgentAdapter -> Agent: AguiAgentAdapter鐨剅un()鏂规硶璋冪敤Agent鐨剆tream()鏂规硶
@enduml